# Summary
Local evaluation in Amplitude Experiment runs evaluation logic directly in the SDK without network requests, providing sub-millisecond performance for latency-sensitive systems, supporting consistent bucketing and targeting segments but lacking Amplitude ID resolution and user enrichment capabilities that remote evaluation offers.

